# Project Rules

Before starting any session, read and follow `.aicontext/prompts/start.md`.

## Prompts

Reusable prompts are available in `.aicontext/prompts/`. When the user says `use <name>`, read `.aicontext/prompts/<name>.md` and follow the instructions in it. For example, `use resume-task` reads and follows `.aicontext/prompts/resume-task.md`.

